(Ii) The advertising uses tools that allow the so-called “retargeting” or allow the user of the Services user to view, while browsing, promotional communications consistent with previously visited sites. The “retargeting” uses cookies and navigation data related to user identity. These cookies, typically profiling, are not directly controllable by the Holder which can therefore not guarantee regarding the use that third parties make of the information collected. The advertising companies also allow you to give up receiving targeted ads, if desired. This does not prevent the setting of cookies, but cuts the use and collection of some data by these companies.
